fields.name: Starbucks® Cold Brew Coffee
fields.description: Handcrafted in small batches daily, slow-steeped in cool water for 20 hours, without touching heat—Starbucks® Cold Brew is made from our custom blend of beans grown to steep long and cold for a super-smooth flavor.

fields.name: Strawberry Açaí Lemonade Starbucks® Refreshers Beverage
fields.description: Sweet strawberry flavors, passion fruit and açaí notes balanced with the delightful zing of lemonade, served over ice with freeze-dried strawberry pieces. The ultimate pick-me-up your afternoon is calling for.

fields.name: White Chocolate Mocha
fields.description: Our signature espresso meets white chocolate sauce and steamed milk, and then is finished off with sweetened whipped cream to create this supreme white chocolate delight.

fields.name: Caffè Latte
fields.description: Our dark, rich espresso balanced with steamed milk and a light layer of foam. A perfect milk-forward warm-up.

fields.name: Birthday Cake Pop
fields.description: Bite-sized vanilla cake mixed with vanilla buttercream, dipped in pink chocolaty icing and topped with white sprinkles.

fields.name: Butter Croissant
fields.description: Classic butter croissant with soft, flaky layers and a golden-brown crust.

fields.name: Big Mac
fields.description: Ever wondered what's on a Big Mac®? The McDonald's Big Mac® is a 100% beef burger with a taste like no other. The mouthwatering perfection starts with two 100% pure all beef patties and Big Mac® sauce sandwiched between a sesame seed bun. It’s topped off with pickles, crisp shredded lettuce, finely chopped onion, and a slice of American cheese. It contains no artificial flavors, preservatives, or added colors from artificial sources. Our pickle contains an artificial preservative, so skip it if you like.

fields.name: McChicken
fields.description: It’s a classic for a reason. Savor the satisfying crunch of our juicy chicken patty, topped with shredded lettuce and just the right amount of creamy mayonnaise, all served on a perfectly toasted bun.

fields.name: McDouble
fields.description: The classic McDouble® burger stacks two 100% pure beef patties seasoned with just a pinch of salt and pepper. Wondering what the difference is between a McDouble® and a Double Cheeseburger? A slice of cheese! It’s topped with tangy pickles, chopped onions, ketchup, mustard and a melty slice of American cheese. The McDouble® contains no artificial flavors, preservatives or added colors from artificial sources. Our pickle contains an artificial preservative, so skip it if you like.

fields.name: 20 Piece McNuggets
fields.description: Enjoy tender, juicy Chicken McNuggets® with your favorite dipping Sauces. Wondering what are McDonald's Chicken Nuggets made of? Chicken McNuggets® are made with all white meat chicken and no artificial colors, flavors, or preservatives.

fields.name: French Fries
fields.description: McDonald's World Famous Fries® are made with premium potatoes such as the Russet Burbank and the Shepody. With 0g of trans fat per labeled serving, these epic fries are crispy and golden on the outside and fluffy on the inside.

fields.name: Strawberry Banana Smoothie
fields.description: The McCafé® Strawberry Banana Smoothie recipe features the perfect combination of real strawberry and banana fruit purees and juices, blended with creamy low fat yogurt and ice.

fields.name: Crunchwrap Supreme
fields.description: A flour tortilla layered with seasoned beef, warm nacho cheese sauce, a crispy tostada shell, crispy lettuce, ripe tomatoes and topped with cool sour cream all wrapped in our signature crunchwrap fold and grilled to go.

fields.name: Chicken Quesadilla
fields.description: An extra flour tortilla filled with melty three-cheese blend, fire grilled chicken, creamy jalapeño sauce folded and grilled to perfection.

fields.name: Beefy 5-Layer Burrito
fields.description: A warm tortilla is covered in a layer of warm nacho cheese and topped with seasoned beef, refried beans, cool sour cream and shredded cheddar cheese. Then it's wrapped creating a layer of nacho cheese all around the outside of the burrito.

fields.name: Nachos BellGrande®
fields.description: A portion of crispy tortilla chips topped with warm nacho cheese sauce, refried beans, seasoned beef, ripe tomatoes and cool sour cream.

fields.name: Nacho Cheese Doritos® Locos Tacos
fields.description: A crunchy taco shell made from Nacho Cheese Doritos® is filled with seasoned beef, crispy lettuce, and pico de gallo.

fields.name: MTN DEW® Baja Blast® Freeze
fields.description: Mountain Dew® Baja Blast in a frozen slushy drink.

fields.name: Chick-fil-A® Chicken Sandwich
fields.description: A boneless breast of chicken seasoned to perfection, freshly breaded, pressure cooked in 100% refined peanut oil and served on a toasted, buttered bun with dill pickle chips. Also available on a multigrain bun.

fields.name: Spicy Chicken Sandwich
fields.description: A boneless breast of chicken seasoned with a spicy blend of peppers, freshly breaded, pressure cooked in 100% refined peanut oil and served on a toasted, buttered bun with dill pickle chips. Also available on a multigrain bun.

fields.name: Spicy Deluxe Sandwich
fields.description: A boneless breast of chicken seasoned with a spicy blend of peppers, hand-breaded, pressure cooked in 100% refined peanut oil and served on a toasted, buttered bun with dill pickle chips, green leaf lettuce, tomato and Pepper Jack Cheese. Gluten-free bun or multigrain bun also available at an additional cost.

fields.name: Cobb Salad
fields.description: Chick-fil-A® Nuggets, freshly breaded and pressure-cooked, sliced and served on a fresh bed of mixed greens, topped with roasted corn kernels, a blend of shredded Monterey Jack and Cheddar cheeses, crumbled bacon, sliced hard-boiled egg and grape tomatoes. Prepared fresh daily. Served with Charred Tomato and Crispy Red Bell Peppers. Pairs well with Avocado Lime Ranch dressing.

fields.name: Chick-fil-A® Nuggets
fields.description: Bite-sized pieces of boneless chicken breast, seasoned to perfection, freshly breaded and pressure cooked in 100% refined peanut oil. Available with choice of dipping sauce.

fields.name: Frosted Lemonade
fields.description: This refreshing treat is a hand-spun combination of Chick-fil-A® Lemonade (or Diet Lemonade) and our signature Icedream® dessert.

fields.name: Baconator®
fields.description: A half-pound* of fresh beef, American cheese, 6 pieces of crispy Applewood smoked bacon, ketchup, and mayo. Carnivores rejoice!

fields.name: Spicy Chicken Sandwich
fields.description: A juicy chicken breast marinated and breaded in our unique, fiery blend of peppers and spices to deliver more flavor inside and out, cooled down with crisp lettuce, tomato, and mayo. It’s the original spicy chicken sandwich, and the one you crave.

fields.name: French Fries
fields.description: Natural-cut, skin-on, sea-salted fries served hot and crispy. The world loves them for a reason.

fields.name: 10 PC. Crispy Chicken Nuggets
fields.description: 100% white-meat chicken breaded to crispy perfection and served with your choice of 6 dipping sauces including Buttermilk Ranch, BBQ, Sweet & Sour, Honey Mustard, or Ghost Pepper Ranch. They’re trending in our restaurants and Twitter feed alike.

fields.name: Parmesan Caesar Salad
fields.description: Made fresh daily with romaine lettuce, grilled chicken breast, Italian cheeses, crunchy Parmesan crisps, and creamy Caesar dressing. One bite will tell you why it’s king of more than just the Romaines.

fields.name: Strawberry Lemonade
fields.description: Cool off with a blend of real strawberries combined with our All-Natural Lemonade for a refreshing taste. Made with premium squeezed lemons, taste why real ingredients lead to better quality.

fields.name: Whopper®
fields.description: A ¼ lb* of flame-grilled beef with juicy tomatoes, crisp lettuce, creamy mayonnaise, ketchup, crunchy pickles, and sliced white onions on a toasted sesame seed bun. *Weight based on pre-cooked patty.

fields.name: 9 Pc. Chicken Fries
fields.description: Breaded, crispy white meat chicken perfect for dipping in any of our delicious dipping sauces.

fields.name: Impossible™ Whopper®
fields.description: A flame-grilled, plant-based patty with juicy tomatoes, crisp lettuce, creamy mayonnaise, ketchup, crunchy pickles, and sliced white onions on a toasted sesame seed bun. *Patty cooked on the same broiler as beef patties.

fields.name: Whopper® Jr. with Cheese
fields.description: One flame-grilled beef patty topped with melty American cheese, juicy tomatoes, crisp lettuce, creamy mayonnaise, ketchup, crunchy pickles, and sliced white onions on a sesame seed bun.

fields.name: 8 Pc. Fiery Chicken Nuggets
fields.description: Burger King’s new Fiery Nuggets start with our classic white meat chicken nuggets, tossed in a spicy glaze for added flavor and heat!

fields.name: Frozen Coke®
fields.description: The great taste of Coca-Cola® in a refreshing frozen drink.

fields.name: Jumbo Jack®
fields.description: 100% beef seasoned as it grills, lettuce, tomato, pickles, onions, ketchup & mayo on a buttery bakery bun. *Jumbo isn't one of those ironic nicknames.

fields.name: Jack's Spicy Chicken® w/ Cheese
fields.description: 100% all white meat spicy crispy chicken fillet with melty Swiss style cheese, tomato, lettuce & mayo on a toasted buttery bakery bun. Yes, please.

fields.name: Jr. Jumbo Jack® Cheeseburger
fields.description: Anywhere else this Jr. Jack would be senior. Because there is nothing junior about this honest-to-goodness 100% beef patty seasoned as it grills topped with American cheese, tomato, pickle, lettuce, and chopped onions--with the just-right amount of ketchup and real mayonnaise. But here? It's got some growing up to do.

fields.name: Jumbo Breakfast Platter w/ Bacon
fields.description: Scrambled eggs, hash browns, 8 mini pancakes, and 3 slices of hickory smoked bacon. Tell your stomach to make room. Pronto.

fields.name: Loaded Breakfast Sandwich
fields.description: Freshly cracked eggs, hickory smoked bacon, grilled ham, grilled sausage & melty American cheese on toasted sourdough bread. Boom, loaded.

fields.name: Strawberry Red Daze Red Bull Infusion w/ Red Bull® Energy
fields.description: A refreshing & energizing iced beverage infused with mixed berry flavors. Made to order with Red Bull® Energy Drink. *Contains Artificial Flavors*

fields.name: Chipotle Chicken Avocado Melt
fields.description: Smoked, pulled chicken raised without antibiotics, smoked Gouda, fresh avocado and cilantro, zesty sweet Peppadew™ peppers and chipotle sauce on Black Pepper Focaccia. Allergens: Contains Wheat, Milk, Egg

fields.name: Homestyle Chicken Noodle Soup
fields.description: Tender pieces of white-meat chicken simmered in a rich, perfectly seasoned homestyle chicken bone broth with curly egg noodles, sliced carrots, celery and herbs. Allergens: Contains Wheat, Egg

fields.name: Strawberry Poppyseed Salad with Chicken
fields.description: Chicken raised without antibiotics, romaine, mandarin oranges and fresh strawberries, blueberries and pineapple tossed in poppyseed dressing and topped with toasted pecan pieces.

fields.name: Strawberry Banana Smoothie
fields.description: A mix of fruit purees and juice concentrates, blended with a banana and plain Greek yogurt and ice.

fields.name: Broccoli Cheddar Soup
fields.description: Chopped broccoli, shredded carrots and select seasonings simmered in a velvety smooth cheese sauce.

fields.name: Pepperoni Flatbread Pizza
fields.description: Thick sliced Pepperoni, fresh mozzarella and our shredded Fontina and mozzarella cheese blend with tomato bell pepper sauce on our flatbread.

fields.name: #9 Hot Pastrami
fields.description: 1/4 lb. of West Coast pastrami with yellow mustard. Served TOGO'S Style

fields.name: #24 Turkey & Avocado
fields.description: 1/4 lb. of whole breast turkey & fresh avocados. Served TOGO'S Style

fields.name: #3 Turkey & Cheddar
fields.description: 1/4 lb. of whole breast turkey & cheddar. Served TOGO'S Style, hot or cold

fields.name: #26 Turkey, Ham & Cheddar
fields.description: 1/4 lb. combination of premium meats. Served TOGO'S Style, hot or cold

fields.name: Santa Fe Chicken Salad
fields.description: Avocado, tomatoes, black bean & corn salsa, cheddar cheese, tortilla strips & pepitas dressing.

fields.name: Cookies
fields.description: Chocolate chunk & peanut butter, individually wrapped

fields.name: Half Dozen Donuts
fields.description: Share the joy by bringing people together with an assortment of half dozen or dozen donuts made in these delicious varieties*: Glazed, Double Chocolate, Strawberry Frosted, Vanilla Frosted, Chocolate Frosted, Old Fashioned, Boston Kreme, Glazed Chocolate Cake, Powdered, Vanilla Creme, Glazed Blueberry, and Jelly.

fields.name: Dozen Donuts
fields.description: Share the joy by bringing people together with an assortment of half dozen or dozen donuts made in these delicious varieties*: Glazed, Double Chocolate, Strawberry Frosted, Vanilla Frosted, Chocolate Frosted, Old Fashioned, Boston Kreme, Glazed Chocolate Cake, Powdered, Vanilla Creme, Glazed Blueberry, and Jelly.

fields.name: Iced Latte
fields.description: Made with milk and blended with our rich espresso, our Iced Latte is the perfect balance of cool, creamy and smooth to get you goin'.

fields.name: Original Blend Iced Coffee
fields.description: Freshly brewed and full of flavor, our Iced Coffee is the perfect pick-me-up any time of day or night, giving you the boost you need to keep on running.

fields.name: Cold Brew
fields.description: An ultra-smooth, full-bodied coffee like no other. Craft-brewed in small batches. Limited quantities available daily.

fields.name: Iced Cappuccino
fields.description: Our Iced Cappuccino is brewed with freshly ground espresso beans and then blended with milk served over ice for a refreshing cup of frothy and bold deliciousness.

fields.name: Classic Assorted Dozen
fields.description: An assortment of our classic doughnuts, selected just for you.

fields.name: Original Glazed® Dozen
fields.description: A dozen of our iconic Original Glazed®doughnuts

fields.name: Coffee Brew Box
fields.description: 96 ounces of fresh brewed coffee. Your Brew Box will arrive with 10 cups, lids, sleeves and stir sticks. 20 creamers and sugars and 10 Splenda® sweeteners.

fields.name: Specialty Dozen with M&M'S®
fields.description: Specialty Dozen made with M&M’S® Contains: 4 Chocolate Iced Doughnut topped with M&M’S®4 Peanut Butter Kreme™ Filled Doughnut topped with M&M’S®4 Original Glazed® Doughnuts.

fields.name: 16 Count Assorted Minis
fields.description: This assortment features 16 of our mini doughnuts. Each box includes 4 Strawberry Iced minis with sprinkles, 4 chocolate iced minis topped with M&M's®, 4 of our traditional chocolate iced minis, & 4 Original Glazed® minis.
